General.Name: Duearity AB
General.Description: Duearity AB (publ), a medical technology company, engages in the development of Tinearity, a tinnitus aid. The company's Tinearity transmits white noise using bone conduction technology to the inner ear in order to relieve symptoms. It also develops Tinearity AI, an artificial intelligence to help people anticipate the symptoms and overcome their problems. The company was incorporated in 2020 and is based in Malmö, Sweden.
